  "detailed_description": "Nova: Cloudwalker's Tale is a charming puzzle game where you move, combine and walk on clouds to gather star shards and make your way through the skies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950490/extras/13cfb75b47e7272e2454e3b35e290c03.poster.avif?t=1695657565\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950490/extras/13cfb75b47e7272e2454e3b35e290c03.webm?t=1695657565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950490/extras/13cfb75b47e7272e2454e3b35e290c03.mp4?t=1695657565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore over 70 levels carefully crafted to challenge you with unique puzzle mechanics.<br></li><li>Make use of 4 types of clouds: rearrange and merge them to make your way across the skies.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950490/extras/2e749ab90359c55f2c296ec61f76ab6f.poster.avif?t=1695657565\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950490/extras/2e749ab90359c55f2c296ec61f76ab6f.webm?t=1695657565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950490/extras/2e749ab90359c55f2c296ec61f76ab6f.mp4?t=1695657565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Travel over 4 unique dreamlike regions as The Cloudwalker in your journey to reunite the lost star shards.<br></li><li>Rich, atmospheric presentation of a devastated fantasy land, with stunning visuals and evocative music. <br></li><li>Enjoy non-linear exploration of a world full of 